			<p class="aboutUsTitle">About Us</p>
			<div class="animate__animated animate__fadeInLeft">
			<p class="aboutUsText">Welcome to the Leicester Film Society, where a passion for movies unites us all!  Join us every Monday for a dose of movie magic, where our film selections are curated through member votes, ensuring a dynamic range that caters to all tastes. But that's not all – our calendar is packed with exciting social events throughout the year. From sophisticated pub quizzes to thrilling bar crawls and exclusive group cinema outings (with sweet discounts for members), we've got your entertainment covered. Have questions? Reach out to us via email or follow us on social media for updates. Let's celebrate the love of film and community together!</p>
			</div>
		</div>
